{"tid":1089411,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"香港流亡商人大瘤","createTime":"2019-04-02T19:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T06:25:47.000Z","uid":190320,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ead75982f1e7d0904e6594b2c421b2472b5c9366","tid":1089411,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T19:13:58.000Z","msg":"坐係押返香港既囚車,諗唔到自己走佬來到巴拿馬,最終都係難逃法網比人捉返返去。<br />\n諗返起當年玩明星既剌激,頓時感慨萬分。<br />\n<br />\n大瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 塞一個比一千萬<br />\n向來精打細算既關,知道呢次機會難得,聽到咁好搵就即刻心雄提出要求。<br />\n關之淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我要塞夠半打 <br />\n大瘤隨即攞出一個高爾夫球,塞入關之淋下體,關之淋雖然痛,但仍強忍住痛楚叫大劉塞第二個。<br />\n大瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 塞入啲啦,你個閪夠大既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n關之淋: 唔得啦,無位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 點會唔得,成個BB都塞得入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n關之淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 好痛呀...呀...啊....唔得啦...唔好呀<br />\n大瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 收得我錢,就要比足服務同誠意.<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (大力塞)<br />\n關之淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:啊!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果,塞到關陰道撕裂出血,痛到佢即刻叫救命,大瘤為免搞出人命先肯收手，之後車左佢去瑪麗睇急症。本來基於病人保密既原則係唔會有一知，奈何其中一個護士睇到,忍唔住大瘤所為先同其他相熟既護士提起,就係咁就傳到傳媒入面。"},{"pid":"a65008690db0c3334ca4a029ebd415c0788b760b","tid":1089411,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:22:27.000Z","msg":"關係咪關x座亨x"},{"pid":"1118508738b8453a9ca3e42e3494f5f7a504fe92","tid":1089411,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:25:20.000Z","msg":"我都有聽d師姐講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0941040b42a5fd2d4bd28b522c213cef0059c5","tid":1089411,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:25:57.000Z","msg":"個護士有冇被消失"},{"pid":"dd2b0acdae5149b82f33ccd518cca5b27b22b4dd","tid":1089411,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🏌️&zwj;♂️</span>"},{"pid":"4ca04513314b29b4d474401056b241d81444de52","tid":1089411,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f0941040b42a5fd2d4bd28b522c213cef0059c5","tid":1089411,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:25:57.000Z","msg":"個護士有冇被消失"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:58:43.000Z","msg":"無人知,不過我相信大瘤無咁神通廣大知道邊個護士當值,而且人咁多無人會知來源"},{"pid":"76538828212b4172e0ec195b73da06f5399a35ab","tid":1089411,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1118508738b8453a9ca3e42e3494f5f7a504fe92","tid":1089411,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:25:20.000Z","msg":"我都有聽d師姐講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"你係護士????"},{"pid":"0f630fc27d2b87a56104b2fa359e627426fbd54c","tid":1089411,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd2b0acdae5149b82f33ccd518cca5b27b22b4dd","tid":1089411,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla